@node MAIN
@title "FloatingClock help"
Well this little program has been a few months in the making, between exams
and job hunting.  I have had a few suggestions from people who have used
previous versions and I hope that this version is the last for a
while since it is now running very smooth, and there doesn't seem to be any
bugs left. (confidence or what! ;-) )  Enjoy.

